text: Nystalea is a genus of moths of the family Notodontidae erected by Achille Guenée in 1852. ==Selected Species== *Nystalea indiana Grote, 1884 *Nystalea collaris Schaus, 1910 *Nystalea eutalanta Dyar, 1921 *Nystalea ebalea (Stoll, [1780]) *Nystalea nyseus (Cramer, 1775) *Nystalea congrua (Dyar, 1908) *Nystalea aequipars Walker, 1858 *Nystalea superciliosa Guenée, 1852 *Nystalea guttiplena Walker, 1857 *Nystalea inchoans Walker, 1857 *Nystalea attenuata Walker, 1858 *Nystalea seminivea (Walker, 1869) *Nystalea ocellata Walker, 1865 ==References== Category:Notodontidae
title: Nystalea
